HEADWORD: Geognosy
<hw>Ge*og"no*sy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>ge`a</grk>, <grk>gh^</grk>, the earth + <grk>gnw^sis</grk> knowing,
